_sText:
This is a submission for our clan member map for {cDS}, Cyber Death Squad.
For more information on this topic see:
http://cyberdeathsquad.com/forums/index.php?topic=8935.0

This map contains 4 sections, the front entrance, the art gallery, the loading dock and the upper level atrium.

Each of the "paintings" in the map would be replaced by a Steam ID tag from our members list, in the maps final format.  The map currently has our founders tags on a rotating cube in the center, as well as large version of our clan logo.  There is also one painting with my Steam ID tag inserted.

The art gallery is a maze setup, while the front and rear sections are straight through sniping zones.   The large upper atrium area is a shoot'em out section with only sparse cover.  The atrium also has jump down access into the gallery.

Questions remain on whether the map is too big for gungame.  We could remove any combination of the front, rear or atrium areas.
